defaultThe panel also considered the recommendations of the PCC in appointing his Deputy (after an open selection and appointment process) and Chief of Staff. The Panel interviewed both appointees robustly before confirming the appointments. The Panel has been equally robust in reviewing the Commissioner’s reports to them and in 
defaultquestioning the information contained within those reports.
