default8.2 There is a 
defaultpresumption in favour of transparency.  
defaultThis incorporates conforming with legislation requirement
defaults
default in respect of publishing information
default and more
default.  I
defaultt also relates to the way in which that information is published.  It needs to be accessible in a format that is easy for the user to access, analyse, understand, and use.  It is these principles that we have applied to our approach to ensuring transparency within 
defaultPolice and Crime Commissioner
default’
defaults Office in 
defaultDyfed-Powys, and one that we are promoting within the police service.
